divs: Sighting DetailsI watched your video- impressive! I think personally it was an unidentified object. I am writing you this note because I noticed something you may have not noticed in your video. I see the black dot in the sky after you trying to film (while talking to your neighbor) and then- I noticed around 1:24 or 1:25 into the film that you are looking downward at your device and your thumb is on the screne, at that point a black object passes between your thumb & head and it looks like the black dot taking off quickly. I wonder myself if that was what that was!? Awesome video capture! I am not a mufon investigator or professional, so I myself dont know what it was actually. I can say ive had some experiences myself before that have left me with no answers and only wondering. I wish you luck in finding out what it might have been:)
Summary: To the Gentleman from TN- Object while filming Dogs- Black disc/sphere in sky
